title: 03/05/21 DPS Hour 2 Tim MacMahon

description:
Tim MacMahon talks to Dan about trades in the NBA. Tim says that he would not say that the Rockets quit on Harden; but Tim says that it was the moves that Harden wanted that have the Rockets in the condition they are in now.
